Text:
Resources for folks experiencing a mental health crisis:

@988Lifeline: call or text 9-8-8 or visit https://t.co/Np4bCYJEbw

@TransLifeline: call 877-565-8860

@Lines_for_Life: for those in Oregon, visit https://t.co/AjbKUW1egL for information on Lines for Life hotlines

The Inflation Reduction Act is the largest climate action since the Clean Air Act, but it must only be the beginning.

@POTUS: declare a climate emergency to unlock the authorities of the International Emergency Economic Powers Act.
https://t.co/fVGk9qXcGi

Congratulations to the Starbucks workers in Eugene on their unanimous vote to unionize last week!
@SBWorkersUnited 
https://t.co/FwtTJvUXLq

Solidarity with the Starbucks workers in Oregon filing for union membership for better working conditions and a livable wage. I’ll continue to fight for the #PROAct to make it easier for everyone to organize at work.
@SBWorkersUnited 
https://t.co/8NUA3ZxO03

Here are some resources for folks who are in crisis:

@800273TALK: 1-800-273-8255
En Español: 1-888-628-9454
For Deaf &amp; Hard of Hearing: 1-800-273-8255
(TTY users: use your preferred relay service or dial 711 then 1-800-273-8255)
@CrisisTextLine: Text HOME to 741741

Candidate Biden was right to pledge to end new fossil fuel permitting on public lands and waters.

This report omits how drilling for oil and gas in federal lands and waters fuels our climate crisis.

@POTUS: We must quit digging the climate chaos hole deeper. Stop leasing now!

We must also have the second bill which addresses:
climate;
housing and forest infrastructure;
education;
child care;
and the biggest middle-class tax cut ever!

Abolishing slavery cannot come with exceptions.

@RepNikema and I introduced the #AbolitionAmendment to finally remove the clause in our 13th Amendment that allows for slavery “as a punishment for crime.”

#EndTheException https://t.co/Td7CNtsKDl

Wow. Stunning illustration of the power of unions to deliver for the people. 

We’ve got to pass the #PROAct.
@AFLCIO @OregonAFLCIO https://t.co/hq6R7DfM2g

Kids deserve the opportunity to play school sports with their friends. ALL kids.

@mPinoe—thank you for speaking out. Everyone in this country deserves equal dignity, respect, and opportunity. #LetKidsPlay

https://t.co/UYhhYUyKc5
